We also got tips on how to dress a woman like Jennifer Lopez - with a big bust, wide hip and narrow waist - pretty and figure accented, without making her too provocative.
For example, if the difference between waist and hips is so big that the skirt or pants really do not fit, you should have at least one piece cut to measure.
